Set torque limits

Usage: wheelctl safety limit [OPTIONS] <DEVICE> <TORQUE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>  Device ID or name
  <TORQUE>  Maximum torque in Nm

Options:
      --global      Apply to all profiles
      --json        Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -v, --verbose...  Verbose logging
  -h, --help        Print help
